    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, add the <strong>chopped lemongrass </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to<strong> </strong>the pan with your <strong>soy sauce</strong>,<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the <strong>coriander & lemongrass oil</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant and the meat-free patties are cooked through – this is your<strong> lemongrass meat-free meat</strong></p>",
